video.title: Miss in Kiss
video.synopsis: A quirk of fate sends an ordinary, sweet-natured high school girl and her father into the home of the school genius, on whom she has a huge crush.

episodes.synopsis: Yue-qin works up the nerve to confess her feelings to her longtime crush, ace student Zhi-shu, only to be humiliated in front of the whole school.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: A freak accident at the lab has devastating consequences for Yue-qin and her father. But soon an old family friend steps up with a generous offer.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: As Yue-qin adjusts to her awkward new living situation, Zhi-shu's cold behavior prompts her to make a startling announcement at school.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Using the photo as leverage, Yue-qin convinces Zhi-shu to help her study for the exam. Meanwhile, Ah-jin resolves to find out where she's living.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Yue-qin worries about Zhi-shu after he stays up late to tutor her. The exam results set the school abuzz. Mrs. Jiang discovers the gossip page.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Ah-jin defends Yue-qin from a con artist, a family dinner takes a surprising turn, and Yue-qin and Zhi-shu face a night alone together in the house.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: As the school break ends, Class F swimming champ Ah-jin recruits Yue-qin for a relay race -- not realizing they'll be competing against Zhi-shu.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: With the college entrance exam looming, Ah-jin prepares soups and study sessions for his friends, only to find they want help from someone else.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: After surprising the Jiangs with New Year's gifts, Yue-qin makes Zhi-shu a good-luck charm for the exam. But it doesn't have the desired effect.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: Yue-qin falls ill on the morning of another big college exam, complicating Zhi-shu's plans. Ah-jin cooks up a romantic scheme for graduation day.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: At the graduation party, Yue-qin grows tired of Zhi-shu's constant insults and decides to play her trump card -- with surprising results.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: Yue-qin joins the college tennis club to keep an eye on Zhi-shu and her new romantic rival, the talented Zi-yu. But the training proves intense.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: Just as Yue-qin begins taking a class with Zhi-shu, she discovers that her days living under the same roof with him may be numbered.
episodes.title: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: Yue-qin's skills are put to the test as she's roped into a doubles match with Zhi-shu and ordered to cook for the whole team at tennis boot camp.
episodes.title: Episode 14

episodes.synopsis: As boot camp winds down, Yue-qin makes a confession to her teammates and finds new inspiration on the court. She and Zhi-shu come home to a surprise.
episodes.title: Episode 15

episodes.synopsis: When Zhi-shu agrees to go on a date with Zi-yu, Mrs. Jiang sends Yue-qin to spy on them in disguise. Meanwhile, Ah-jin investigates a troubling rumor.
episodes.title: Episode 16

episodes.synopsis: Yue-qin takes Zhi-shu on a dreamy outing, the Jiangs welcome a new member of the household, and Ah-jin makes big plans for the campus festival.
episodes.title: Episode 17

episodes.synopsis: Zi-yu's visit to the Jiangs' home proves disastrous for Yue-qin. Rivalries heat up as Ah-jin and the tennis club set up booths at the campus festival.
episodes.title: Episode 18

episodes.synopsis: A surprising scene unfolds at the campus goddess contest. As Yue-qin and the Jiangs plan a winter spa trip, Ah-jin takes on a new culinary challenge.
episodes.title: Episode 19

episodes.synopsis: Plagued with doubts about his path in life, Zhi-shu makes a big decision that catches everyone off guard. A photo from the spa upsets Ah-jin.
episodes.title: Episode 20

episodes.synopsis: Feeling lost without Zhi-shu, Yue-qin jumps at the chance to find out where he works. But she's not the only one determined to stay close to him.
episodes.title: Episode 21

episodes.synopsis: As Yue-qin sinks into depression, her worried friends confront Zhi-shu. A crisis at the Old Lunar Tree gives Ah-jin a chance to play hero.
episodes.title: Episode 22

episodes.synopsis: While Ah-jin plots to save the tree, Yue-qin learns Zhi-shu has received an offer from overseas. A storm shakes up everyone's Valentine's Day plans.
episodes.title: Episode 23

episodes.synopsis: Yue-qin spends an awkward evening with Zhi-shu, Ah-jin braves the storm to make good on his promise, and a new contest springs up on the gossip page.
episodes.title: Episode 24

episodes.synopsis: A worried Yue-qin rushes Yu-shu to the hospital and calls Zhi-shu for help. Ah-jin prepares for his moment of glory at the red ribbon ceremony.
episodes.title: Episode 25

episodes.synopsis: Yue-qin gains another suitor, while Zi-yu contends with a mysterious stalker. A spooky encounter at the hospital puts Yu-shu and Nuo on edge.
episodes.title: Episode 26

episodes.synopsis: Yue-qin and the Jiangs rally around the ailing Nuo. Zi-yu's sister sets a mischievous plan in motion. At Mrs. Jiang's urging, Yue-qin goes on a date.
episodes.title: Episode 27

episodes.synopsis: A new job proves challenging for Yue-qin. When Zhi-shu and Zi-yu head to the coast over summer break, Yue-qin and the Jiangs follow close behind.
episodes.title: Episode 28

episodes.synopsis: After fleeing the photo shoot in a huff, Yue-qin bumps into a familiar face on the beach. Zhi-shu sets a trap for Zi-yu's stalker.
episodes.title: Episode 29

episodes.synopsis: Tensions between the Wu sisters heat up, Zhi-shu asks a rival for a favor, and Yue-qin's 20th birthday party yields several sweet surprises.
episodes.title: Episode 30

episodes.synopsis: As everyone makes plans for Christmas, Yue-qin starts working at her father's restaurant to save up for a special present for Zhi-shu.
episodes.title: Episode 31

episodes.synopsis: After a bitter fight with his parents, Zhi-shu lets Yue-qin in on a secret. Mrs. Jiang realizes Yu-shu knows something she doesn't.
episodes.title: Episode 32

episodes.synopsis: On Valentine's Day, Yue-qin overhears a revealing conversation between Zhi-shu and Zi-yu. Mr. Jiang makes an upsetting discovery.
episodes.title: Episode 33

episodes.synopsis: A guilt-stricken Zhi-shu offers to help out at his father's company. For his first professional meal, Ah-jin prepares dishes inspired by Yue-qin.
episodes.title: Episode 34

episodes.synopsis: Yue-qin spends summer break at the toy company, where she strikes up an unlikely friendship. Zhi-shu searches for inspiration for a new product line.
episodes.title: Episode 35

episodes.synopsis: Zhi-shu announces he has a plan to solve the company's money problems. Mrs. Jiang, Yue-qin and Zi-yu team up to sabotage a meeting with the Bais.
episodes.title: Episode 36

episodes.synopsis: To force herself to move on from Zhi-shu, Yue-qin goes on a date with Ah-jin. Mr. Jiang comes home from the hospital to a surprise.
episodes.title: Episode 37

episodes.synopsis: While Yue-qin weighs an offer from Ah-jin, Zhi-shu and Sha-sui face pressure from Mr. Bai. Zhi-shu has a profound experience at the Old Lunar Tree.
episodes.title: Episode 38

episodes.synopsis: As Yue-qin's father says goodbye to the Jiangs, Zhi-shu interrupts with an announcement. Soon everyone is abuzz with new plans for the future.
episodes.title: Episode 39
